WEBVTT

01:37.100 --> 01:41.020
[The Best Thing]

01:41.470 --> 01:48.570
[Episode 14: Citrus Peel—Bitter, spicy, and warm in nature.
It regulates qi, strengthens the spleen, reduces dampness, and transforms phlegm.]

02:01.590 --> 02:03.790
Later, his girlfriend got

02:03.790 --> 02:05.310
an opportunity to study abroad,

02:05.760 --> 02:07.510
so she broke up with Senior He.

02:08.210 --> 02:10.330
And after leaving the country, she never came back.

02:13.150 --> 02:15.190
You were already so insecure in a long-distance relationship,

02:16.190 --> 02:17.120
let alone an international one.

02:18.370 --> 02:19.410
Get real.

02:22.870 --> 02:24.710
Senior He has always been a very gentle

02:24.710 --> 02:25.940
and kind person,

02:26.120 --> 02:27.360
but that doesn't mean you can

02:27.360 --> 02:28.370
treat him casually.

02:36.290 --> 02:37.290
Remember to take your medicine on time.

02:44.480 --> 02:45.270
Shen Xifan.

02:46.400 --> 02:48.000
It's not easy to find someone

02:48.000 --> 02:49.400
who genuinely cares for you.

02:49.880 --> 02:51.079
Can you stop

02:51.079 --> 02:52.590
pushing him away, okay?

03:22.270 --> 03:23.340
I'm sorry.

03:22.510 --> 03:28.740
♫It's fate, it must be fate♫

03:29.320 --> 03:35.940
♫It's fake, it must be fake♫

03:30.520 --> 03:32.000
I'm sorry.

03:51.200 --> 03:58.040
♫Far, away, we part, our ways♫

03:58.070 --> 04:04.540
♫But I, still linger, for nights and days♫

04:04.840 --> 04:11.540
♫When you're away♫

04:12.320 --> 04:19.290
♫When you're away♫

04:59.610 --> 05:01.800
You caught a cold? I'll turn up the air conditioner temperature for you a bit.

05:01.830 --> 05:02.910
Let me know if you're cold.

05:03.530 --> 05:04.120
Thank you.

05:29.510 --> 05:30.310
He, you're here!

05:30.310 --> 05:31.160
He, you're back?

05:36.830 --> 05:37.800
He came back.

05:41.040 --> 05:42.040
Don't rush!

05:42.040 --> 05:42.750
This is for you.

05:42.750 --> 05:44.040
You didn't need to bring so many gifts!

05:44.040 --> 05:45.190
I just picked up some health products,

05:45.190 --> 05:46.920
and the toys are for the children.

05:46.920 --> 05:48.240
Kids, come on, come on!

05:49.050 --> 05:49.870
Come home!

05:50.560 --> 05:52.070
Come and get the toys. Let's distribute them together.

05:52.070 --> 05:53.040
Your dad is over there.

05:54.270 --> 05:55.390
He, you're back, huh?

05:56.600 --> 05:57.159
Carry on.

05:57.159 --> 05:57.800
Okay, okay.

05:57.800 --> 05:58.159
Continue.

05:58.159 --> 05:59.630
You guys keep talking.

06:01.950 --> 06:03.120
Why did you arrive so late?

06:04.160 --> 06:05.190
I just finished work

06:05.560 --> 06:07.600
and then caught the latest flight here.

06:08.480 --> 06:09.280
Have you eaten?

06:09.800 --> 06:10.710
Not yet.

06:10.760 --> 06:11.250
It's okay.

06:11.360 --> 06:13.340
I'll ask your aunt to make some late-night snacks for you later.

06:13.580 --> 06:15.290
No need. I can just find something to eat myself.

06:15.320 --> 06:16.440
You don't need to find food elsewhere yourself.

06:16.460 --> 06:17.670
We have everything at home.

06:19.630 --> 06:20.390
You've caught a cold?

06:20.630 --> 06:21.120
It's nothing.

06:21.240 --> 06:21.950
Just a minor cold.

06:22.190 --> 06:24.480
The toys Uncle gave us are awesome!

06:24.870 --> 06:25.830
Then, I'll go upstairs to rest first.

06:27.820 --> 06:28.550
Wait a moment.

06:28.920 --> 06:29.870
Come here, come here, come here.

06:30.020 --> 06:31.170
Perfect timing.

06:31.870 --> 06:33.070
Let me...

06:33.710 --> 06:34.830
introduce you.

06:35.230 --> 06:36.860
This is Nurse Wang from our hospital.

06:37.830 --> 06:39.710
She's staying with us for the New Year this year.

06:40.680 --> 06:43.190
This is my son, He Suye, whom I've often mentioned to you.

06:46.000 --> 06:46.630
Nice to meet you.

06:47.510 --> 06:48.240
Nice to meet you.

06:48.380 --> 06:49.409
Let me introduce you.

06:49.830 --> 06:50.630
This is my son,

06:50.630 --> 06:51.310
Wang Chang.

06:51.480 --> 06:52.520
Chang, say hello.

06:53.240 --> 06:54.040
Hello, Uncle.

06:55.159 --> 06:55.750
No, that's not right.

06:55.770 --> 06:56.690
You should call him "Brother."

06:56.830 --> 06:57.600
It's alright.

06:58.190 --> 06:59.390
You can just call me "Dr. He."

07:03.240 --> 07:04.240
Hello, Dr. He.

07:09.480 --> 07:11.870
Then... I'll go upstairs to rest first.

07:11.870 --> 07:12.600
Okay.

07:13.720 --> 07:14.270
Oh, right.

07:15.070 --> 07:17.000
They're staying

07:17.000 --> 07:18.090
in your old room this year.

07:18.360 --> 07:20.000
Why don't you stay on the first floor?

07:25.000 --> 07:25.390
Okay.

07:25.600 --> 07:26.190
Okay.

07:29.000 --> 07:29.800
Then...

07:43.360 --> 07:44.240
That's just how he is.

07:45.450 --> 07:47.870
Why don't you find his aunt

07:48.260 --> 07:49.240
and ask her to fix him some late-night snacks,

07:49.240 --> 07:50.190
and you can help?

07:50.190 --> 07:51.000
Okay.

07:51.600 --> 07:52.390
Let's go, son.

07:54.110 --> 07:54.990
Mom.

07:55.490 --> 07:56.760
I want toys too.

07:59.310 --> 08:00.070
Son,

08:00.360 --> 08:02.270
when we get back to Bei City, Mom will buy you some, okay?

08:02.830 --> 08:03.510
Alright.

08:03.510 --> 08:04.310
Good boy.

08:04.500 --> 08:05.290
Let's go.

09:24.370 --> 09:30.730
[Jiangzhou Bank wishes you a happy birthday.]

09:38.080 --> 09:41.600
[Jiangzhou Unicom: Dear Unicom user, happy birthday.]

10:11.250 --> 10:11.670
New Year's bonus for everyone!

10:11.670 --> 10:12.360
Really?

10:12.360 --> 10:13.240
Of course, it's real.

10:13.240 --> 10:16.480
Come on, come on!

10:16.480 --> 10:17.270
Wait a moment!

10:17.270 --> 10:18.720
Come on, come on!

10:18.720 --> 10:19.440
Wait, wait, wait!

10:19.440 --> 10:20.270
Let me say a few words first.

10:20.750 --> 10:22.600
Thank you all for your hard work over the past year!

10:22.600 --> 10:23.360
Applause!

10:23.870 --> 10:24.630
Applause!

10:25.910 --> 10:27.150
With everyone's support,

10:27.420 --> 10:28.970
we've been able to manage such a large

10:28.990 --> 10:29.960
Gunan Huating Hotel!

10:30.480 --> 10:32.720
In the new year, I'll still be counting on all of you!

10:32.790 --> 10:33.240
Okay!

10:33.550 --> 10:34.030
Okay.

10:34.390 --> 10:35.790
Here are the red packages with bonuses, one for each person.

10:35.790 --> 10:36.600
Happy New Year!

10:37.000 --> 10:38.550
Okay, thank you, Manager Cheng!

10:38.550 --> 10:39.600
May you look radiant this year!

10:39.600 --> 10:40.120
Thank you.

10:40.120 --> 10:41.000
Wishing you a sweet life!

10:41.000 --> 10:41.630
Thank you!

10:41.870 --> 10:43.550
May all your wishes come true!

10:44.320 --> 10:46.030
Happy New Year!

10:46.270 --> 10:47.080
May you eat and sleep well!

10:47.390 --> 10:48.390
Happy New Year! Happy New Year!

10:48.630 --> 10:51.720
General Manager, may you become more and more handsome in the new year

10:51.750 --> 10:53.270
and grow to 1.88 meters tall soon!

10:53.270 --> 10:55.120
I also hope you become even more handsome than me.

10:55.910 --> 10:56.600
Keep up the good work.

10:59.210 --> 11:00.450
Look at what you made!

11:00.480 --> 11:01.270
Public resources.

11:01.270 --> 11:03.120
What kind of dumpling is this?

11:03.120 --> 11:03.910
All the filling has fallen out.

11:04.270 --> 11:05.120
You should be fined for this.

11:05.120 --> 11:05.870
How embarrassing!

11:12.900 --> 11:14.330
Take it, take it!

11:14.360 --> 11:15.790
Happy New Year!

11:16.870 --> 11:18.440
Hurry up, hurry up!

11:18.440 --> 11:18.910
Okay.

11:18.910 --> 11:20.720
Come on, come on!

11:20.720 --> 11:22.120
Everyone, let's count down together: three, two, one.

11:22.270 --> 11:23.320
Three, two, one.

11:23.320 --> 11:25.790
Happy New Year!

11:30.270 --> 11:31.510
Happy New Year, Xifan.

11:31.910 --> 11:32.670
See you next year.

11:33.120 --> 11:35.870
See you next year. Go home and get some good rest.

11:37.320 --> 11:38.670
You should go home and rest early today as well.

11:39.120 --> 11:41.520
Alright, I'll dutifully finish my last shift.

11:42.120 --> 11:42.870
Xiangya?

11:43.080 --> 11:44.360
Text me when you land, okay?

11:44.360 --> 11:45.150
Just to let me know you arrived safely.

11:48.840 --> 11:49.670
I'm back, bye-bye.

11:49.670 --> 11:50.160
Bye-bye.

11:55.600 --> 11:56.910
Let's go. I'll take you to the airport.

11:57.670 --> 11:59.310
No need. I can grab a cab myself.

11:59.440 --> 12:01.150
It's New Year's. There aren't many drivers available.

12:02.540 --> 12:03.080
Let's go.

12:24.270 --> 12:25.670
Happy New Year, Grandma.

12:26.050 --> 12:28.170
-Happy New Year.
-Happy New Year.

12:31.850 --> 12:33.730
You look even more beautiful in the new year.

12:33.760 --> 12:35.460
Thank you.

12:41.150 --> 12:42.080
Hurry up and drink.

12:42.670 --> 12:44.200
What are you guys doing over there?

12:44.480 --> 12:45.390
Come on, drink up, drink up.

12:45.390 --> 12:46.630
Everyone to the table, to the table.

12:49.910 --> 12:50.720
The dish is here!

12:50.720 --> 12:51.320
The dish is here!

12:51.900 --> 12:52.900
There are more dishes coming.

12:55.440 --> 12:55.910
Okay.

12:56.510 --> 12:57.600
Let's eat together.

12:57.600 --> 12:59.030
I'll join you later. There's more to come.

12:59.160 --> 13:00.030
You go ahead and attend to them first.

13:00.030 --> 13:00.870
Alright, you go ahead then.

13:01.030 --> 13:01.660
Okay.

13:09.610 --> 13:10.660
It's alright, it's alright.

13:10.790 --> 13:13.050
Breaking things brings peace. Breaking things brings peace.

13:13.160 --> 13:16.070
A New Year's Eve dinner wouldn't be complete without soup.

13:16.110 --> 13:18.290
Sheng, look what your wife did!

13:19.080 --> 13:19.870
It's the New Year, after all.

13:19.870 --> 13:20.670
Make another pot.

13:20.670 --> 13:21.550
Forget it. Forget it.

13:21.550 --> 13:22.510
It's nothing.

13:22.510 --> 13:23.510
It's not a big deal.

13:23.510 --> 13:24.150
It's fine.

13:24.690 --> 13:25.620
Let me tell you...

13:31.560 --> 13:32.170
Sheng,

13:32.470 --> 13:34.200
it's really impressive

13:34.200 --> 13:35.240
that our town has produced

13:35.240 --> 13:36.240
such an outstanding doctor like you!

13:37.790 --> 13:38.470
Well,

13:38.490 --> 13:40.810
we'll be counting on you for our medical care from now on.

13:40.840 --> 13:41.840
Sheng!

13:45.040 --> 13:46.830
Why talk about illness on New Year?

13:47.640 --> 13:50.110
We should say we'll all be

13:50.360 --> 13:51.720
relying on Sheng for our long lives.

13:51.720 --> 13:52.550
Right, right, right.

13:52.550 --> 13:54.320
That's right, Sheng, we're all counting on you.

13:54.320 --> 13:55.030
Okay, okay.

13:55.030 --> 13:55.600
Sheng...

14:15.950 --> 14:16.810
Mom, hurry up.

14:18.200 --> 14:19.240
Dinner is ready!

14:19.240 --> 14:20.390
It's New Year's!

14:24.310 --> 14:25.590
Drinking this again?

14:25.870 --> 14:26.600
It's New Year's today.

14:26.600 --> 14:27.240
I can drink this, right?

14:27.240 --> 14:28.260
Yes, yes.

14:29.000 --> 14:30.910
Ms. Shen can drink a little today.

14:31.300 --> 14:31.900
It's okay. It's okay.

14:31.930 --> 14:32.690
Come on.

14:32.720 --> 14:33.720
This one for Ms. Shen.

14:36.650 --> 14:37.440
Let me say something.

14:39.960 --> 14:41.000
Time flies by quickly.

14:42.200 --> 14:43.440
The years wait for no one.

14:44.390 --> 14:45.460
On this...

14:46.240 --> 14:47.800
day of family reunion,

14:48.670 --> 14:50.790
first, I wish our Ms. Liu,

14:50.790 --> 14:52.320
in the new year,

14:52.320 --> 14:53.390
safety and health,

14:54.030 --> 14:54.840
beauty like a flower,

14:54.840 --> 14:55.600
and a return to eighteen.

14:56.540 --> 14:57.440
So sweet.

14:57.440 --> 14:59.440
And I also wish our Ms. Shen

14:59.790 --> 15:01.150
everything goes smoothly

15:01.150 --> 15:02.270
and wealth rolls in.

15:02.270 --> 15:03.270
Get rich quickly.

15:03.550 --> 15:05.670
May your wish to get rich quickly come true soon!

15:07.120 --> 15:09.670
Finally, I wish for our family of three

15:09.670 --> 15:11.000
to be happy and fulfilled.

15:11.440 --> 15:12.480
Even though

15:12.710 --> 15:14.760
you'll be studying abroad soon,

15:15.640 --> 15:17.590
our family of three will always

15:17.610 --> 15:18.690
remain connected in heart.

15:19.360 --> 15:21.080
Let's make a wish for your father too.

15:21.080 --> 15:23.390
May your father's cooking get better and better,

15:23.390 --> 15:25.000
and feed our Ms. Shen well,

15:25.000 --> 15:25.510
okay?

15:25.510 --> 15:25.870
Okay.

15:25.870 --> 15:26.320
Okay!

15:26.320 --> 15:26.720
Okay.

15:26.720 --> 15:26.960
Come on.

15:26.960 --> 15:27.510
Come on.

15:28.240 --> 15:28.670
Cheers!

15:28.670 --> 15:31.000
-Cheers!
-Happy New Year!

15:34.720 --> 15:36.150
Happy New Year, Third Uncle.

15:36.150 --> 15:37.550
I'm here to wish you a Happy New Year.

15:42.940 --> 15:45.830
[Yan Heng]

15:47.640 --> 15:48.520
Happy New Year.

15:48.540 --> 15:49.490
Wishing you happiness every day,

15:49.750 --> 15:50.360
Xifan.

15:56.620 --> 15:59.300
[Add to blacklist]

16:01.120 --> 16:02.600
Oh, I'm especially happy

16:02.630 --> 16:04.480
for the New Year this year.

16:04.480 --> 16:06.870
Our He family has two great doctors!

16:06.870 --> 16:07.360
That's right.

16:07.360 --> 16:08.320
One is Sheng,

16:08.320 --> 16:10.480
and the other is his son, Suye, right?

16:10.480 --> 16:11.320
Yes, yes, yes.

16:11.320 --> 16:13.550
They both came back for New Year's this year, right?

16:13.550 --> 16:14.320
It's so rare.

16:14.320 --> 16:15.600
Especially Sheng.

16:15.880 --> 16:17.280
He even brought Wang back!

16:18.320 --> 16:20.870
Our whole family is reunited! Come on, come on!

16:20.870 --> 16:21.440
Cheers, cheers!

16:21.440 --> 16:23.320
May everyone have an even better year ahead.

16:23.320 --> 16:24.510
Better and better.

16:28.240 --> 16:28.720
Sheng,

16:28.720 --> 16:30.910
-you must drink more today.
-Eat up.

16:30.910 --> 16:31.550
Ah, okay.

16:44.300 --> 16:45.780
Your new look is really handsome.

16:45.810 --> 16:48.090
In the new year, may you be like Sun Wukong,

16:48.110 --> 16:49.190
healthy and lively.

16:54.990 --> 16:57.240
Mom said to let you pay New Year's respects

16:57.240 --> 16:59.080
to the auntie who sent the toys on my behalf

16:59.080 --> 17:00.330
to thank her for her encouragement.

17:00.810 --> 17:01.530
Okay.

17:13.480 --> 17:15.000
Hey, pour the wine, pour the wine.

17:15.000 --> 17:16.960
Zhao Ze, the one you gave the Transformer to before,

17:16.960 --> 17:19.030
asked me to wish you a Happy New Year on his behalf.

17:19.829 --> 17:20.510
Okay.

17:22.349 --> 17:24.160
Cheers, cheers.

17:25.720 --> 17:26.440
Please.

17:26.839 --> 17:28.280
Thank you, Mr. Shen.

17:28.310 --> 17:29.110
We don't have room for it.

17:29.110 --> 17:29.960
We've just finished dinner.

17:30.660 --> 17:31.770
Oh, alright, alright.

17:31.830 --> 17:32.790
Just have a small bite.

17:32.790 --> 17:33.880
I'll eat it later.

17:45.160 --> 17:47.270
Look at the clothes that the actor was wearing just now.

17:47.270 --> 17:48.590
This is it.

17:48.590 --> 17:49.310
You've drunk so much.

17:49.310 --> 17:50.240
Have another drink.

17:50.440 --> 17:51.440
Here, have some water first.

17:51.440 --> 17:51.830
Hurry.

17:52.350 --> 17:53.000
After drinking some water...

17:53.000 --> 17:53.550
I'm fine.

17:53.550 --> 17:54.880
I'll help you into the room.

17:54.880 --> 17:55.430
He?

17:56.110 --> 17:56.750
He?

17:58.240 --> 18:00.110
It's okay. I'll take care of him.

18:00.110 --> 18:01.240
You should take the child and go upstairs now.

18:01.240 --> 18:02.110
Don't catch a cold.

18:02.640 --> 18:03.200
Okay.

18:03.720 --> 18:04.830
Then, tell him to drink more water.

18:04.830 --> 18:05.720
Alright, alright.

18:05.720 --> 18:06.400
Don't worry.

18:06.880 --> 18:07.650
Chang,

18:08.310 --> 18:09.240
let's not eat anymore.

18:09.680 --> 18:11.440
Mom will take you upstairs to bed, okay?

18:11.440 --> 18:11.920
Dad?

18:13.680 --> 18:14.160
Dad.

18:15.920 --> 18:16.640
Dad?

18:19.350 --> 18:20.790
Come on, have some water, have some water.

18:22.550 --> 18:23.680
Don't choke, come on.

18:25.920 --> 18:26.850
It'll help clear your head a bit.

18:31.880 --> 18:32.720
I drank too much.

18:35.950 --> 18:37.270
I've been saying that...

18:40.350 --> 18:41.160
All gone?

18:44.640 --> 18:45.590
Drink some water.

18:53.290 --> 18:56.290
Everyone seems... quite happy.

18:59.640 --> 19:01.270
I wanted to ask you something.

19:02.570 --> 19:04.400
I heard you have a girlfriend now.

19:07.480 --> 19:09.550
No, they're just making that up.

19:12.120 --> 19:13.500
Hurry up.

19:15.310 --> 19:16.200
Let me tell you.

19:16.940 --> 19:18.220
For a man, you know,

19:18.520 --> 19:19.890
you should get married first

19:19.920 --> 19:21.230
and then establish your career.

19:23.320 --> 19:25.120
When I was your age,

19:26.030 --> 19:26.990
how old were you at that time?

19:27.340 --> 19:28.250
You were already 8 years old.

19:32.240 --> 19:33.030
9 years old.

19:33.310 --> 19:34.240
8!

19:37.580 --> 19:38.450
Fine, 8 it is.

19:41.330 --> 19:42.130
9, then.

19:47.260 --> 19:48.740
How's work lately?

19:50.960 --> 19:51.750
It's okay.

19:52.000 --> 19:53.400
What do you mean by "okay"?

19:54.510 --> 19:55.830
I've heard everything.

19:56.270 --> 19:58.790
The funding for this year's research project

19:59.310 --> 20:00.510
hasn't been approved yet, right?

20:01.850 --> 20:02.640
Am I right?

20:06.880 --> 20:08.570
And your grandfather isn't helping you either.

20:09.680 --> 20:10.680
Though he can't really help with that.

20:12.590 --> 20:13.350
You

20:13.350 --> 20:14.830
just didn't listen to me

20:15.310 --> 20:17.030
and insisted on studying TCM.

20:19.920 --> 20:21.240
You even selected

20:21.480 --> 20:23.160
such an unconventional research focus.

20:24.590 --> 20:27.440
If you had listened to me earlier, it wouldn't have come to this.

20:28.850 --> 20:30.170
But it's not too late now.

20:30.790 --> 20:32.310
Be a good boy and listen to me.

20:33.830 --> 20:36.190
After the New Year, I'll use my connections for you.

20:36.440 --> 20:37.490
You can go into...

20:38.480 --> 20:39.610
pharmaceutical research and development.

20:40.400 --> 20:41.720
The work is easier,

20:42.230 --> 20:45.230
and the salary is much, much higher than

20:45.310 --> 20:47.310
what you earn at that small clinic each week.

20:54.200 --> 20:55.000
Yeah.

20:56.200 --> 20:58.330
I guess when it comes to getting married first and then establishing a career,

20:58.540 --> 21:01.010
I'm definitely far behind you.

21:05.620 --> 21:06.420
How about this?

21:08.110 --> 21:09.550
From now on, I won't come back for New Year's.

21:10.070 --> 21:12.400
I'll spend New Year's with my grandfather in Hang City. How's that?

21:32.490 --> 21:34.040
My son has grown up.

21:43.110 --> 21:45.680
My son has truly grown up.

22:49.140 --> 22:51.900
He asked me to wish you a Happy New Year on his behalf.

23:37.180 --> 23:39.050
Why are you suddenly video-calling me?

23:39.640 --> 23:40.550
I missed you.

23:42.880 --> 23:43.600
Suye!

23:43.920 --> 23:46.240
Happy New Year, and wishing you wealth and prosperity!

23:46.720 --> 23:47.590
Happy New Year.

23:48.750 --> 23:50.680
Are you alone in the room?

23:52.680 --> 23:55.070
I just finished eating and came back to rest.

23:56.680 --> 23:57.790
Where are you dining?

23:58.000 --> 24:00.850
At Chun's, my dad booked a private room a month in advance.

24:01.070 --> 24:02.440
They have many new dishes this year.

24:02.440 --> 24:03.400
I've heard they're quite delicious.

24:03.400 --> 24:04.440
That sounds nice.

24:04.720 --> 24:05.960
When you come back, we'll come here again together.

24:06.750 --> 24:07.550
Okay.

24:08.240 --> 24:09.030
Grandpa?

24:09.890 --> 24:11.240
Which dish do you like the most?

24:11.310 --> 24:12.400
Among their new dishes,

24:12.400 --> 24:13.880
there's a fish soup that's quite good.

24:14.070 --> 24:16.110
Add some vinegar, and it's very appetizing.

24:16.160 --> 24:17.480
You should try it when you come back.

24:18.490 --> 24:20.010
Suye, we have to go now.

24:20.310 --> 24:22.240
Grandpa Yu, come on, let's continue the meal.

24:24.670 --> 24:25.230
Alright.

24:26.750 --> 24:28.350
After I come back in a couple of days,

24:28.350 --> 24:29.480
I'll come to your house for New Year's greetings.

24:29.750 --> 24:31.680
Okay, welcome, welcome.

24:31.910 --> 24:33.110
Welcome, welcome.

24:33.130 --> 24:35.520
Suye, I won't say much more.

24:36.510 --> 24:38.110
Enjoy your time over there.

24:38.500 --> 24:40.580
You only visit there a few days each year, right?

24:41.030 --> 24:42.470
No matter what happens,

24:42.490 --> 24:43.620
just smile and let it go.

24:44.830 --> 24:46.160
Happy New Year to you.

24:47.920 --> 24:48.830
Happy birthday.

24:51.440 --> 24:52.310
Thank you, Grandpa.

24:54.310 --> 24:54.940
Bye-bye.

24:54.960 --> 24:55.480
Bye-bye.

25:37.390 --> 25:39.590
Zhao Ze, the one you gave the Transformer to before,

25:40.160 --> 25:42.480
asked me to wish you a Happy New Year on his behalf.

25:57.400 --> 25:59.030
Happy New Year.

26:11.890 --> 26:12.930
Happy New Year.

26:13.370 --> 26:15.570
Congratulations to the little one on his recovery,

26:15.830 --> 26:18.590
and to Dr. He for his benevolence and excellent medical skills.

26:19.030 --> 26:21.920
In the new year, I wish Dr. He peace and joy,

26:22.120 --> 26:24.360
may everything go well, and may your healing hands continue to work wonders.

26:33.680 --> 26:34.960
That sounds

26:35.070 --> 26:36.750
a bit too formal, doesn't it?

27:58.240 --> 27:58.680
Hello?

28:03.170 --> 28:04.000
Happy New Year.

28:08.270 --> 28:09.270
Happy New Year.

28:11.750 --> 28:12.830
Why did you...

28:13.590 --> 28:15.510
suddenly call me?

28:20.200 --> 28:21.830
Didn't you wish me that everything goes well?

28:22.550 --> 28:24.590
This is one of those things.

28:27.750 --> 28:28.970
I'm not disturbing you, am I?

28:30.070 --> 28:30.640
No.

28:31.880 --> 28:32.680
That's good then.

28:44.070 --> 28:44.830
What...

28:46.200 --> 28:47.440
what are you doing?

28:49.350 --> 28:51.640
I'm at home watching the Spring Festival Gala with my parents.

28:52.720 --> 28:53.510
How about you?

28:57.070 --> 28:57.920
I...

28:58.520 --> 28:59.770
I just got back to my hometown

28:59.920 --> 29:01.440
and finished the New Year's Eve dinner with my relatives.

29:01.760 --> 29:02.810
I've just returned to my room.

29:04.460 --> 29:05.790
You went back to your hometown?

29:07.880 --> 29:09.790
Yes, I forgot to tell you that.

29:11.620 --> 29:12.310
It's okay.

29:19.440 --> 29:20.350
He Suye.

29:21.440 --> 29:23.020
When you come back after the New Year,

29:23.250 --> 29:25.600
you'll receive our company's New Year gift box.

29:26.000 --> 29:27.070
Thanks to you,

29:27.070 --> 29:29.720
this year's medicinal cuisine for the New Year's Eve dinner has been especially popular.

29:29.720 --> 29:30.720
It sold very well.

29:31.880 --> 29:32.670
Is that so?

29:33.310 --> 29:34.110
That's good then.

29:46.810 --> 29:48.860
Your hometown is in Hu City, right?

29:50.070 --> 29:51.070
Yeah.

29:51.360 --> 29:52.230
How did you know?

29:53.200 --> 29:55.450
When you signed the consulting contract before,

29:55.680 --> 29:59.640
I vaguely remembered seeing it on your ID card.

30:01.790 --> 30:03.350
Yes, I almost forgot.

30:15.170 --> 30:16.540
My parents are calling me.

30:16.920 --> 30:19.480
Then, I'll go out and join them.

30:22.350 --> 30:23.140
Okay.

30:24.590 --> 30:25.310
Okay.

30:30.480 --> 30:31.270
Shen Xifan?

30:38.640 --> 30:41.030
I wish you, in the new year...

30:43.450 --> 30:44.380
that all your dreams come true...

30:46.320 --> 30:47.990
and that everything goes as you desire.

30:58.600 --> 31:00.070
Then I also wish you...

31:01.400 --> 31:02.510
in the new year,

31:03.550 --> 31:05.070
that all your dreams come true...

31:06.670 --> 31:07.800
and that everything...

31:08.590 --> 31:10.270
goes as you desire.

32:37.160 --> 32:40.270
♫Happy birthday to you♫

32:41.030 --> 32:44.310
♫Happy birthday to you♫

32:45.310 --> 32:49.270
♫Happy birthday to you♫

32:50.910 --> 32:54.580
♫Happy birthday to you♫

32:55.400 --> 32:58.820
♫Happy birthday to you♫

32:59.790 --> 33:03.920
♫Happy birthday to you♫

33:04.590 --> 33:09.350
♫Happy birthday to you♫

33:14.270 --> 33:14.880
He Suye.

33:17.350 --> 33:18.400
Happy birthday.

33:19.440 --> 33:20.350
Make a wish.

33:23.350 --> 33:24.960
You know what my wish is.

33:26.440 --> 33:27.060
Okay.

33:35.920 --> 33:36.920
I've made my wish.

33:38.200 --> 33:39.010
How am I supposed to

33:39.570 --> 33:40.650
blow out this candle?

33:45.000 --> 33:46.200
Just give it a blow.

33:47.070 --> 33:47.710
Okay.

34:01.030 --> 34:02.030
Happy birthday.

34:02.480 --> 34:04.810
Congratulations on growing another year older.

34:29.460 --> 34:30.540
I can finally see it clearly.

34:36.110 --> 34:37.070
I'm sorry.

34:37.360 --> 34:39.560
This is all I have at home right now.

34:39.710 --> 34:41.440
I couldn't buy a cake during the New Year holiday.

34:41.440 --> 34:42.550
It's a bit simple.

34:48.320 --> 34:51.480
What made you decide to celebrate my birthday?

35:18.570 --> 35:19.740
I'll be back on the third day of the New Year.

35:23.070 --> 35:23.880
What?

35:25.030 --> 35:26.030
I said...

35:28.320 --> 35:29.360
I'll be back on the third day of the New Year.

35:31.740 --> 35:38.050
♫You're like a gentle wind♫

35:38.500 --> 35:44.050
♫After early summer afternoon, it blows past my heart♫

35:45.360 --> 35:51.560
♫When your fingers touch my hands♫

35:52.290 --> 35:56.910
♫So you're also here for me♫

35:59.310 --> 36:04.900
♫I hear you say, red beans grow in the southern lands♫

36:00.950 --> 36:01.760
Happy New Year.

36:03.400 --> 36:04.480
In the new year...

36:05.440 --> 36:06.440
things will only get better.

36:05.880 --> 36:08.740
♫When spring comes, a few branches begin to sprout♫

36:09.280 --> 36:12.740
♫Cherish the youth♫

36:14.590 --> 36:20.510
♫Loving you is the best thing I've ever done♫

36:21.480 --> 36:26.350
♫Among the vast sea of people, you and I understand each other♫

36:28.210 --> 36:34.130
♫Missing you is the most beautiful thing in my life♫

36:35.070 --> 36:40.280
♫Write it down in your heart and never disappear♫

37:11.000 --> 37:11.670
Morning.

37:14.360 --> 37:15.110
Good morning.

37:20.110 --> 37:21.150
Are you going out?

37:23.280 --> 37:24.480
Just going for a walk around town

37:24.760 --> 37:26.800
to see if anyone needs medical help.

37:33.320 --> 37:34.110
Let's have breakfast.

38:57.670 --> 38:58.360
He,

38:58.360 --> 38:59.440
thank you so much.

38:59.440 --> 39:00.150
My mother's leg

39:00.180 --> 39:01.110
has been hurting all winter.

39:01.110 --> 39:02.110
She couldn't even walk anymore.

39:02.110 --> 39:02.800
How much do you charge?

39:02.800 --> 39:03.710
That's not necessary.

39:03.710 --> 39:04.760
It was just a simple acupuncture treatment.

39:04.760 --> 39:07.070
No charge. Just tell your mother to be more careful from now on.

39:07.960 --> 39:08.630
Well, thank you then.

39:09.510 --> 39:10.400
-Happy New Year.
-Happy New Year.

39:10.400 --> 39:11.030
I'm off then.

39:11.030 --> 39:11.800
Goodbye.

40:10.240 --> 40:13.400
♫A light scent♫

40:17.860 --> 40:22.110
♫Slowly awakening my heart♫

40:22.600 --> 40:26.770
♫The elusive little mist appears and disappears♫

40:27.680 --> 40:34.270
♫Quietly entering your world, your memories♫

40:35.640 --> 40:38.520
♫The unexpected encounter with the wind♫

40:41.450 --> 40:46.060
♫Layer by layer, rendering the air♫

40:47.880 --> 40:52.240
♫The whispers that are sometimes far, sometimes near♫

40:52.750 --> 40:58.140
♫Exchanging our hidden secrets♫

40:59.720 --> 41:04.890
♫Using my breath♫

41:06.070 --> 41:11.990
♫To blend the soothing scent of love♫

41:12.160 --> 41:14.880
♫To merge in♫

41:18.050 --> 41:21.240
♫The air♫

41:24.690 --> 41:29.230
♫Shortens the distance between two hearts♫

41:32.180 --> 41:35.650
♫Longing adjusts its frequency♫

41:38.160 --> 41:42.900
♫Resonating with our expectations♫

41:44.530 --> 41:48.620
♫The little challenges that time has given us♫

41:49.490 --> 41:54.780
♫Are meant to deepen the meaning of loving you♫

41:59.780 --> 42:05.040
♫Using my breath♫

42:06.050 --> 42:12.100
♫To blend the soothing scent of love♫

42:12.430 --> 42:15.230
♫To merge in♫
